/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"講得唔好，HKU都有得讀，而且年年都開，但好多人因為覺得難所以唔take，CU就會強制你讀曬佢認為你要識嘅嘢。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔緊要 中大最大 環境贏曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申超級煩膠打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"d3514e189fc0242dc07c2d729560afa42bb6e8fb","tid":745302,"uid":171823,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"首先我唔係好同意方言呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果想知HKU同CU課程嘅分別同埋有咩Courses讀，可以睇呢兩條link去分析下<br />\n<br />\nHKU<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.chinese.hku.hk/handbook/2018_19_handbook.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.chinese.hku.hk%2Fhandbook%2F2018_19_handbook.pdf&d=wCT9IhKfBwynynUE1NkBa0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=656e74f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.chinese.hku.hk/handbook/2018_19_handbook.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nCU<br />\n<a href=\"https://cusis.cuhk.edu.hk/psc/public/EMPLOYEE/HRMS/c/CU_CUR_MENU.CU_ATCH_DISPLAY.GBL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcusis.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fpsc%2Fpublic%2FEMPLOYEE%2FHRMS%2Fc%2FCU_CUR_MENU.CU_ATCH_DISPLAY.GBL&d=wCT9IhKfBwynynUE1NkBa0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=14609f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://cusis.cuhk.edu.hk/psc/public/EMPLOYEE/HRMS/c/CU_CUR_MENU.CU_ATCH_DISPLAY.GBL</a><br />\n<br />\n你會見到CU係強制要你讀 語言、文字、聲韻、文獻、現代文學、古代文學而且文學仲會細拆幾科黎讀，咁你就知CU個基礎係點打。HKU都有相近嘅科，但都係放係高年級嘅課程，無所謂必讀，就算必讀都係2揀1。例如現代漢語入面已經包埋基礎嘅聲韻，古代漢語包基礎嘅文獻學、文字學咁，文學唔會好似CU咁再細分幾類。<br />\n但同時HKU多好多華語文學嘅科，文學批評，仲有依家學術界主流嘅研究，包括性別研究，同埋用比較文學嘅方式睇番中文，呢啲都係CU無嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n如果針對中史嘅話，CU會有史學作為必修科，HKU同樣都係無，中史係1科必修都無。不過HKU嘅中史特點係齊。斷代史同埋專題史幾乎年年都會開齊。CU就係比專題史再specific，會再細緻啲講一個topic。翻譯嘅情況都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你就會見到兩間U嘅分別"}]}